research_municipality_step.notes: Information gathered from the City of Golinda website, Texas Municipal League City Officials Directory, and Texas State Directory Online. There was a discrepancy regarding the Mayor Pro Tem, with some sources listing Tim Harrington and others Bobby Farney; Bobby Farney was chosen based on the City of Golinda's official website and the Texas State Directory. Some sources also indicated potential open council positions, but only named officials are included.
